	    <p>At present, the XCF is seeking project proposals and working on internal infrastructure projects.</p>
	    <p>We are co-sponsoring a
	      <a href="https://decal.ocf.berkeley.edu">
		DeCal on Linux Systems Administration,
	      </a> and run <a href="https://www.peeringdb.com/net/17036">AS26073</a>, an Autonomous System
	        located in the Hurricane Electric FMT2 datacenter announcing several IPv4 and IPv6 prefixes.
	    </p>
	    <p>If you have are interesting in having the XCF sponsor your project, please
	      <a href="#contact">
		contact us.
	      </a>
